Strong tech background with a good understanding of driving integration between systems
Good exposure in the product life cycle and driving execution
Strong communication and evangelization skills to kick off & drive partnerships with other teams
Strong communication and presentation skills. Ability to articulate progress and plans clear to the leadership team and get their feedback
Bachelors in Computer Science or equivalent preferred
